OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a brighter day with
OL,6,Fa mixture of sunny intervals and
OL,7,Foccasional showers, these falling as
OL,8,Fsleet or snow on the hills. Freshening
OL,9,Fwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA few showers this evening,
OL,12,Fbut soon becoming dry with some clear
OL,13,Fspells overnight. Winds easing and
OL,14,Fallowing a touch of frost.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA mainly dry day, bright with
OL,17,Fsome hazy sunny intervals but in
OL,18,Fgeneral a lot of cloud, perhaps a spot
OL,19,For two of rain. Freshening southerly
OL,20,Fwind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
